<h2>Objectives</h2>
<p>After successful completion of this assignment, the student will be able to:</p>
<ul>
<li>Import an Existing Video Clip</li>
<li>Edit the Video Clip</li>
<li>Export the Video Clip for use on the web</li>
</ul>
<hr />
<div class="row">
<div class="col-sm-12">
<h3>Assignment Specifications</h3>

<p>
	In this assignment, you will create a short 15-20 second video using the video editing tools in Photoshop. Use any means you have available to record a clip. The video must have a still title at the beginning, beyond that everything is up to you.
</p>

<p>
	Use the NTSC DV &ndash; 720 x 480 Film &amp; Video preset, and export the finished video as an MPEG-4 (mp4).
</p>

<hr class="line" />

<p>
	Save your files with appropriate names, following the file naming convention:
</p>

<pre><code>
  yourname-video.mp4
</code>
</pre>

<p class="alert alert-success">Once completed, upload your files to <a href="<!-- @video-dropbox -->" target="_top" class="alert-link">Video Dropbox</a>.</p>

